      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new streetwear line that's supposed to be a bit more gritty and \"real.\" i want to make sure i'm capturing the authentic aesthetic of urban culture without it feeling like cheap cultural appropriation. can you describe what that core vibe is like? like, what are the visual elements that actually define that urban look?",
