      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The core vibe is defined by an unpolished, raw authenticity where street-level reality blends into fashion, often emphasizing comfort, utility, and mismatched textures like distressed denim or heavyweight canvas. Visually, this translates to monochromatic palettes with stark contrasts, oversized silhouettes that defy traditional tailoring, and logos that feel hand-placed or intentionally imperfect rather than mass-produced perfection. To honor the culture rather than appropriate it, these elements should feel lived-in and functional, reflecting genuine daily struggles rather than a curated, aestheticized performance of urban life.",
